<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>2026 GOP Senate Priority Survey</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #fffff;
        color: #222;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #d1d1d1;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header img {
        width: 100%;
        display: block;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      td {
        padding: 15px 10px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        vertical-align: middle;
      }
      .question-text {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: bold;
        width: 60%;
      }
      /* Clickable Button Styling */
      .choice-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        margin: 2px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 4px;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      .yes-btn { background-color: #28a745; }
      .no-btn { background-color: #b20000; }
      
      .main-button {
        display: block;
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #b20000;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="https://www.myimgcloud.com/6f5037c7-cc7d-4247-9acc-9d73998291cd.png" alt="GOP Header" />
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p><strong>${Recipient.FIRST_NAME},</strong></p>
        <p>Before we finalize the strategy report heading to President Trump, we need your direct input on these key questions:</p>

        <table>
          <tr>
            <td class="question-text">Do you support a full ban on foreign funding in U.S. elections?</td>
            <td style="text-align: right; white-space: nowrap;">
              <a href="{{survey_link}}&q1=yes" class="choice-btn yes-btn">YES</a>
              <a href="{{survey_link}}&q1=no" class="choice-btn no-btn">NO</a>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="question-text">Should Republicans prioritize more border wall funding in 2026?</td>
            <td style="text-align: right; white-space: nowrap;">
              <a href="{{survey_link}}&q2=yes" class="choice-btn yes-btn">YES</a>
              <a href="{{survey_link}}&q2=no" class="choice-btn no-btn">NO</a>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="question-text">Do you trust the mainstream media’s coverage of GOP candidates?</td>
            <td style="text-align: right; white-space: nowrap;">
              <a href="{{survey_link}}&q3=yes" class="choice-btn yes-btn">YES</a>
              <a href="{{survey_link}}&q3=no" class="choice-btn no-btn">NO</a>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <a href="{{survey_link}}" class="main-button">SEE THE REST OF THE QUESTIONS & SUBMIT SURVEY</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
